node.text:
Hello everyone! Sorry for the spam, this is the last one but we're finally here! My first professional comic is coming out tomorrow.

Who are you rooting for? Harley? Punchline? 

Thank you all for your love and support these past few years. Big things are on the horizon! 

I wouldn't be here without you. Let me know what you thought of the book tomorrow! The team and I did our best and hope you all like it! 

Thanks again and have a great day!

node.text:
ANOTHER BIG NEWS!

@danpgwatters and I bring you Azrael this October in Batman: Urban Legends #8 

I am so proud of this book and I can't wait to show you all "the cooler" Batman in Red! 

-Azrael: Azrael, the last acolyte of the Order of St. Dumas, has returned to the streets of Gotham City after serving with the Justice League in the stars. He's convinced he's strayed too far from his purpose, too far from his teachings, and needs to reassert himself. But he'll be met with a city that's changed forever, a city that will shake his faith.

node.text:
Oh, hey. I'm 27 today. 

Another year, another selfie. Sorry for the lack of uploads and over all presence. 

A lot has happend this year with me. Like most of us, this whole pandemic thing got me in a really bad place mentally. There were a lot of doubts and constant questions of self-worth. I was debating on quiting a couple of times. WOTS wasn't going anywhere and I felt to small to tackle such a big project on my own with my limitted knowledge that I have right now. 

But this year, I made so many new people. People that quickly became my close and dearest friends. They kept my head above the water and because of them, this whole year wasn't as bad as I thought it would be. I learned so much from them, artistically and as a person. You know who you are. 

And finally, at the end of last year, I was offered to join DC.  I still think they've got the wrong guy but I'll try my best to earn it. 

to all of you who keep messaging me and checking up on me, just commenting and even leaving likes on my work, I see you all and really appreciate you. I woun't be here without you. 

Love you all and have a great day. I'll sure try to! <3

-N
